      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Hellfire",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "That dreadful Magnamalo has\r\nbeen spotted! Quick, Hunter,\r\nyou must leap into action at\r\nonce! We cannot allow it to\r\nfeed on the hordes or it may\r\nbecome too powerful to defeat!\r\nNo time to waste! Hop to it-to it!",
        "Target": "Hunt Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Feu de l\u0027enfer",
        "Client": "Hojo le Ma\u00EEtre de la Guilde",
        "Description": "Le terrible Magnamalo a \u00E9t\u00E9 rep\u00E9r\u00E9 !\r\nIl faut que tu t\u0027en occupes au\r\nplus vite ! Nous ne pouvons pas le\r\nlaisser se nourrir des hordes ou il\r\nrisquerait de devenir bien trop\r\npuissant ! Il n\u0027y a pas une\r\nminute \u00E0 perdre ! Allez, zou !",
        "Target": "Chasser le Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Fuoco infernale",
        "Client": "Hojo il capo della Gilda",
        "Description": "Quel terribile Magnamalo \u00E8\r\nstato avvistato. Presto, devi\r\nsubito entrare in azione! Non\r\ndeve nutrirsi delle altre orde\r\naltrimenti diventerebbe troppo\r\nforte. Non c\u0027\u00E8 tempo da\r\nperdere! Su, su!",
        "Target": "Caccia il Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "H\u00F6llenfeuer",
        "Client": "Gildenmeister Hojo",
        "Description": "Der furchtbare Magnamalo wurde\r\ngesichtet! Du musst sofort aktiv\r\nwerden! Wir m\u00FCssen verhindern,\r\ndass er sich an den Horden\r\nweidet, sonst wird er bald zu\r\nm\u00E4chtig! Los, die Zeit dr\u00E4ngt!",
        "Target": "Erjage Magnamalo.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Fuego infernal",
        "Client": "Hojo el maestro del gremio",
        "Description": "\u00A1Han visto a ese condenado\r\nMagnamalo! \u00A1R\u00E1pido, tienes\r\nque hacer algo! \u00A1No podemos\r\npermitir que se alimente de\r\nlas hordas o se har\u00E1 a\u00FAn m\u00E1s\r\nfuerte! \u00A1Venga, no hay tiempo\r\nque perder!",
        "Target": "Caza a Magnamalo",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0410\u0434\u0441\u043A\u043E\u0435 \u043F\u043B\u0430\u043C\u044F",
        "Client": "\u041C\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440 \u0413\u0438\u043B\u044C\u0434\u0438\u0438 \u0425\u043E\u0434\u0437\u0451",
        "Description": "\u041E\u0431\u043D\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0435\u043D \u0436\u0443\u0442\u043A\u0438\u0439 \u041C\u0430\u0433\u043D\u0430\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E!\r\n\u0421\u043A\u043E\u0440\u0435\u0435 \u0432 \u0431\u043E\u0439! \u041D\u0435\u043B\u044C\u0437\u044F, \u0447\u0442\u043E\u0431\u044B \u043E\u043D\r\n\u043F\u043E\u0435\u0434\u0430\u043B \u043C\u043E\u043D\u0441\u0442\u0440\u043E\u0432, \u0430 \u0442\u043E \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0435\u0442\r\n\u043F\u043E\u0437\u0434\u043D\u043E! \u0412\u043F\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0434, \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u0435\u043D\u0438\r\n\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041C\u0430\u0433\u043D\u0430\u043C\u0430\u043B\u043E",
